               <p>My husband's name is 
               <persName id="t17890422-65-person599">
                  John
                   Evans
               <interp inst="t17890422-65-person599" type="surname" value="Evans"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890422-65-person599" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890422-65-person599" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            ; the prisoner came to lodge at our house on the 1st of April, and went away on Friday evening, he never gave us notice; I missed a bed, a bolster, and sheets; and I missed other things which are not in the indictment; he was taken the same evening with the things, and the next morning he was taken before the magistrate.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17890422-65-person600">
                  THOMAS
                   CHIFFIN
               <interp inst="t17890422-65-person600" type="surname" value="CHIFFIN"></interp>
